sentences.english: Results Food-poisoning accidents happen more frequently in the third quarter.
sentences.chinese: 结果食物中毒事故第三季度高发。

sentences.english: Itau and Unibanco release official third-quarter earnings this week.

sentences.english: China's gold demand fell 22% in the third quarter to a four-year low.
sentences.chinese: 第三季度中国黄金需求下降22%，至四年低点。

sentences.english: Coca-Cola reports its third-quarter profits were up 14 percent.
sentences.chinese: 可口可乐公司报告其第三季度利润增长百分之十四。

sentences.english: Third-quarter revenue fell 21% to 19.3 billion euros.
sentences.chinese: 第三季度收入下降21%，至193亿欧元。

sentences.english: Casting a pall over the market is the third-quarter earnings season.
sentences.chinese: 第三季度业绩报告给市场笼罩上了一层阴影。

sentences.english: One is what happened after the third quarter.
sentences.chinese: 第一点便是第三季度之后会发生什么。

sentences.english: But third-quarter advertisingdeclines across the industry appeared to improve.
sentences.chinese: 但是报业第三季度的广告下滑幅度出现好转。

sentences.english: Jobs for photographers grew by about 22 percent in Q3.
sentences.chinese: 第三季度摄影师的工作增长了大约22%。

sentences.english: This directly led to the third quarter of this year, Ping An of China into a net loss .
sentences.chinese: 这直接导致了今年第三季度，平成净亏损为中国的。

sentences.english: The entire fleet is scheduled to complete this upgrade in the third quarter of 2015.
sentences.chinese: 整个机队预定在2015年第三季度完成升级。

sentences.english: During the third quarter of last year, that figure was at 2,110.

sentences.english: Can the third quarter extend the spell?
sentences.chinese: 但第三季度财报季会延续这种势头吗？

sentences.english: Manufacturing production decelerated sharply in the third quarter.
sentences.chinese: 制造业生产指数在第三季度急剧下滑。

sentences.english: The start of production is planned for the third quarter of 2013.
sentences.chinese: 新厂计划在2013年第三季度内点火生产。

sentences.english: The global seismicity in the third quarter of the year 1998 was still of medium level.
sentences.chinese: 1998年第三季度，全球地震活动仍为中等水平。
